|4 |      └─SORT                              |           |1       |60          |
|5 |        └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN                |           |1       |60          |
|6 |          ├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN              |           |2       |35          |
|7 |          │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN             |ITEM       |2       |13          |
|8 |          │ └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE RANGE SCAN|STORE_SALES|2       |16          |
|9 |          └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET         |DT         |1       |16          |
=================================================================================
